{
  "stem": "1172.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, I don't know if my parents really understood what was going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they were reading newspapers, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they never discussed it with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My sister being at work, in forced labor, of course, knew, understood, more about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had no relatives in a foreign country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was no way for us to run away or do anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We just hoped for the best.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And nobody knew really what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody realized that things would be that bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When the deportations started, we would see moving trucks, big moving trucks, coming and picking up people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But, you know, there was a rumor-- oh, you're just being sent to a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we waited till our time came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On September 24th, 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At 11:00 at night, two Gestapo men came, knocked on the door, and told us to pack a few things and come with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister, who worked for this German company, she didn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she volunteered to go with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we packed a few things, and they took us by public transportation to a big synagogue that they had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] pointed out-- had made to a place where they put-- brought all the people that they arrested that night were put into this synagogue.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The seats were all taken out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were sitting on their suit cases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Old people, young people, babies, retarded people, all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we came in there, the SS men in charge called my sister and me up to the bimah-- he was sitting at the bimah-- and asked us several questions.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
